	measure 'T&D UOM' = ```
			
			 
			 VAR _volUOM = CALCULATE(
			    SELECTEDVALUE('T&D'[UOM]),
			        'T&D'[Account] = "Volume")
			
			VAR _cashUOM = IF(_volUOM = "Ktons", "$/tons", IF(_volUOM = "lbs(m)", "ct/lbs"))
			
			RETURN
			SWITCH(
			    SELECTEDVALUE(
			        'T&D Seg'[Accounts]),
			         "Volume", _volUOM, 
			         "Cash Cost", _cashUOM,
			         BLANK())
			```
